---
By: Mencius
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 262
    Verse: 10
Tags:
  - Ignorance
---
To act without clear understanding, to form habits without investigation,
to follow a path all one’s life without knowing where it really leads—such
is the behavior of the multitude.
